_Hif’il_ Imperative for regular shorushim:
The [[{{_Hif’il_ imperative}} form]] follows the following conjugations for [[regular shorushim]]:
|            | *Masculine* | *Feminine* |
| *Singular* | הַבְדֵּל <br> _havdeil!_ <br> [to a man] separate! | הַבְדִּילִי <br> _havdili!_ <br> [to a woman] separate! |
| *Plural*   | הַבְדִּילוּ <br> _havdilu!_ <br> [to men] separate! | הַבְדֵּלְנָה <br> _havdeilnau!_ <br> [to women] separate! |
For any regular shoresh, you can replace the letters ‎ב, ‎ד, and ל above with the letters of your shoresh to produce the proper conjugation.
